window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>\"<i>Joyland</i> is a breathtaking, beautiful, heartbreaking book.... Even the most hardboiled readers will find themselves moved.\" <br>â€”Charles Ardai, Edgar- and Shamus Award-winning editor of Hard Case Crime. </b></p> <p>Set in a small-town North Carolina amusement park in 1973, <i>Joyland</i> tells the story of the summer in which college student Devin Jones comes to work as a carny and confronts the legacy of a vicious murder, the fate of a dying child, and the ways both will change his life forever. <i>Joyland</i> is a brand-new novel and has never previously been published.</p>"; 
